My build of dwm.

Binds:
M + key                 view tag key
M|Ctrl + key            add key to visible tags
M|Shift + key           send curr window to key tag
M|Shift|Ctrl + key      not sure

M + p                   spawns dmenu
M + return              spawns st
M + w                   spawns web browser
M + b                   toggles top bar
M + j                   focus next window
M + k                   focus previous window
M + i                   increases windows in master
M + d                   decreases windows in master
M + l                   increases master width
M + h                   decreases master width
M + tab                 alternate between cur and last tag
M + q                   kill client
M + t                   set tiled layout
M + f                   set float layout
M + m                   set monocle layout
M + space               cycle last layout
M|Shift + space         toggle floating
M + 0                   see all tags
M|Shift + 0             duplicates cur window to all tags?
M + ,                   focus previous monitor
M + .                   focus next monitor
M|Shift + ,             send curr window to prev monitor
M|Shift + .             send curr window to next monitor
M|Shift + q             quit dwm
fn + F6                 mute sound
fn + F7                 decrease sound
fn + F8                 increase sound
fn + F2                 decrease brightness
fn + F3                 increase brightness
